# Executive Overview

NEO TRANSIT X-22 PRO represents the conceptual large-scale evolution of the X-22 transit platform. Whereas X-22 focuses on metropolitan corridors, the PRO architecture expands into multi-corridor, intercity, and megacity transportation networks.

The system introduces:

* NEO CORE QUANTUM NODE governance
* VELOX MAX propulsion architecture
* AFATX atmospheric optimization
* High-density renewable energy routing
* Distributed corridor intelligence
* Dynamic passenger-density balancing

The objective is to create a transportation framework capable of operating as a regional mobility ecosystem rather than a single transit line.

